'''''Star Wars Insider'' 40''' is the fortieth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was published in [[October]]/[[November]] [[1998]]. Two cover variants were available for issue 40: a newsstand version featuring a [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wing]] battle and a subscriber-exclusive cover featuring a [[Single Trooper Aerial Platform/Legends|battle droid]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"From the Editor's Desk"
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Prequel Update]]"
*"[[In the Star Wars Universe|In the ''Star Wars'' Universe]]: [[Richard LeParmentier]]" {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
